name: SuperClean Apartment in A Warm Home
review: Adonis was a very friendly and accommodating host.  His apartment was as described, clean, and quiet.  Check-in and check-out was a breeze.    With a bit of a walk there is convenient train access to Manhattan.   I would happily stay there again.
